org.appspot.apprtc

Interface AppRTCClient.SignalingEvents

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CallActivity, CallNotifyService, CallsActivity, CallsActivityCopy
    Enclosing interface:
    AppRTCClient

    public static interface AppRTCClient.SignalingEvents
    Callback interface for messages delivered on signaling channel.

    Methods are guaranteed to be invoked on the UI thread of |activity|.
